Package: quadprogpp
Type: Package
Title: Quadratic Programming Solver in C++, using QuadProg++ and Eigen Templated Linear Algebra Libraries
Version: 1.1-0
Date: 2015-03-08
Authors@R: c(person("Farzad", "Noorian", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "farzad.noorian@sydney.edu.au"),
			 person("Benjamin", "Stephens", role = c("ctb", "cph")),
			 person("Gael", "Guennebaud", role = c("ctb", "cph")),
			 person("Angelo", "Furfaro", role = c("ctb", "cph")),
			 person("Luca", "Di Gaspero", role = c("ctb", "cph")),
			 person("Berwin", "A. Turlach", role = c("ctb", "cph")),
			 person("Andreas", "Weingessel", role = c("ctb", "cph")))
URL: https://github.com/fnoorian/quadprogpp, http://www.diegm.uniud.it/digaspero/index.php?page=software, http://www.labri.fr/perso/guenneba/code/QuadProg/
Description: A fast Quadratic Programming solver is implemented using C++ solver library QuadProg++, ported to Eigen linear algebra C++ templates, which is optimised by explicit vectorisation for SSE2/3/4. The solver is 4x to 5x faster than the Fortran based quadprog (as of version 1.5-5), as shown in the benchmarks included in the demos.
License: GPL (>= 2.0)
Depends: R (>= 3.0.2), Rcpp (>= 0.11.3)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen (>= 0.3.2.3.0)
